${offset 15}${font DejaVu Sans Mono:size=10}${color EDE0FF}Name               ${alignr}PID   CPU%   MEM%
${offset 15}${color FF7878}${top name 1} ${alignr}${top pid 1} ${top cpu 1} ${top mem 1}
